{"tid":1362949,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民陣稱倘光復元朗不獲批不反對通知　警方可拘捕參與者","createTime":"2019-07-25T04:30:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T08:19:20.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6da16c3c7d7a61c223dab7238b09eec25aedd673","tid":1362949,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:30:50.000Z","msg":"民陣副召集人陳皓桓表示，若星期六的「光復元朗」遊行不獲批不反對通知書，警方可以直接拘捕遊行人士，建議遊行人士帶備攝錄鏡頭及計劃離開路線。<br />\n<br />\n陳皓桓出席一個電台節目時表示，若周六的遊行不獲批不反對通知書，警方可以不配合遊行及不分派人手維持秩序，亦可以直接拘捕並以非法集結等罪名控告遊行人士。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，警方就元朗襲擊事件只拘捕了12人，擔心會再發生白衣人襲擊事件。他強調，警方必須提供合理理由，證明遊行有可能妨礙公眾秩序，才可以拒絕發出不反對通知書。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1470345-20190725.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1470345-20190725.htm&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D5LdSN32AczdJcE5lfwVwJ8%3D&h=d4eaab86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1470345-20190725.htm&h=9afb92ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1470345-20190725.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d0de912abf3857a498a753f9e24e7fb86bec42bf","tid":1362949,"uid":28831,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:31:41.000Z","msg":"714百步梯有不反對通知書都拉啦屌你老母收皮啦"},{"pid":"029eb542abafc86baa15b9cb3b59d660201a238c","tid":1362949,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:19:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}